assertInvocationCount

protected void assertInvocationCount(int count)
Asserts the given test invocation count. This assumes that each test invocation causes exactly one Log entry

assertSequentialExecution

protected void assertSequentialExecution(String... actions)
Asserts sequential execution of the given tests. As a precondition, each test must exhibit an execution time of 500 milliseconds. The assertion then asserts that the time between each test invocation is at least 470 milliseconds.

assertParallelExecution

protected void assertParallelExecution(String... actions)
Asserts parallel execution of the given tests. As a precondition, each test must exhibit an execution time of 500 milliseconds. The assertion then asserts that the time between each test invocation is at most 300 milliseconds.

logEntries

protected Log.Entry[] logEntries(String... actions)
Retrieves the Log entries for all given actions.
